                    <img src="~/assets/images/placeholder_man_profile_pic.jpg" class="card-img-top team-member-img" alt="team member 2">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center">Lukas Deni Posavec</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Curabitur elementum, sapien eget dignissim ultrices, turpis orci ornare massa, at hendrerit velit nibh eu ipsum. Duis eleifend, elit in hendrerit cursus, justo sapien viverra nunc, ac bibendum.</p>
